body: @saeed68gm I'm getting this error with my own project, but the issue is the same . You can look into `tensorflow\contrib\quantize\python\fold_batch_norms.py` to compare the graph structure `graph_matcher` is looking for and what `silm.mobilenetv2.py` created. I had taken a quick glance at `silm.mobilenetv2.py` 's graph but doesn't see anything wrong with it.
